According to the Final Decision Notice issued by Eskom this week, and Eskom spokesperson, Mr Eric Khoza, &#8220;Eskom may, upon 15 calendar days, disconnect the electricity entirely and indefinitely, should the electricity debt situation not improve.Lowvelder previously reported on Eskom&#8217;s intentions when the first notice was published.Also read: Mbombela electricity to be cut due to Eskom debtThe full article, and a list of all the effected areas, will be published in Friday&#8217;s edition of the Lowvelder Newspaper. Get your copy in store, on street, or subscribe to have it delivered to your doorstep.